{"tid":1666390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 連登真係平行時空","createTime":"2019-10-21T03:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T11:20:30.000Z","uid":88169,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"cefe56dad2f2152b768c428f51e80faeb10fcd12","tid":1666390,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BAfnVj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BAfnVj.jpg&h=a6ff4c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾個3毛出po話暴力話恐怖分子又話國際輿論又會失民意<br />\n成班on9又正皮又比人帶左風向<br />\n<br />\n比少少自我思考得唔得呀你班連登仔<br />\n<br />\n講明核彈都唔割，擺個假野又咁撚左膠又話失民意<br />\n<br />\n跟住你望下fb ig 邊撚道有人話暴力，個個都支持不割<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkSmivU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkSmivU.png&h=9a698b61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4b2Npe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4b2Npe.png&h=2559f7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWqZPCA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWqZPCA.png&h=b0f857ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">根本大家同路人都識spin下比黑警，spin下比工聯會，跟住唔割𥱊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地就一野比班3毛帶晒風<br />\n<br />\n自己諗下真係有炸彈想行動升級又比你地阻，下下想人升級又要人跟你地條路行"},{"pid":"7394e1a132f23686e5ef048245cab607f1a6fa88","tid":1666390,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f938939fcc631f5bff3c7e994bb1ed236daa56d2","tid":1666390,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"55aa8fc2155064e76971018391c6be